'''Knight of Griffin's Roost''' is the title held by the head of [[House Connington]], a knightly house that rules the castle of [[Griffin's Roost]] in [[the Stormlands]].

The head of House Connington once held Griffin's Roost as the [[Lord of Griffin's Roost]], but the lordship was stripped from them following [[Robert's Rebellion]].
